verbose_text: To rate protein profiling in response to IFNbeta, both NS5 expressing and vector control cells were harvested postincubation with or without 1000 U/mL IFNbeta for 2 days prior to Western blot with properly diluted antibodies : mouse anti-Flag tag, anti-cyclophilin A (Cell Signaling), anti-calreticulin, and anti-beta actin antibodies (Invitrogen).
